<div class="scene-details">
<h2 class="character-name">Rani</h2>
<div class="role">Director & Creator</div>
<div class="separator"></div>
<div class="character-arc">Rani embarked on his discovery of filmmaking by studying cinema in Seoul, South Korea. Now working as a freelance translator, he spends his free time creating music – or noise – on the piano or computer, gaming late into the night, and delving into literature and philosophy. The discovery of new experiences and impressions through diverse art forms and media is what interests him and what he wishes to convey through his own works.</div>
<a href="https://www.swissfilms.ch/en/person/gillioz-rani/320F8A74646E41718A8CB4BD0C32B79A" class="credits-link" target="_blank"><span class="link-text">View Portfolio</span><span class="link-line"></span></a>
