<div class="scene-details">
<h2 class="character-name">Layal</h2>
<div class="role">Technology & Organisation</div>
<div class="separator"></div>
<div class="character-arc">Meet Layal, our data magician! She's all about bringing data to life with a dash of creativity and a sprinkle of magic. Enjoying animated and superhero movies, Layal's passion shines through in her work as a data scientist and econometrician. Whether she's jazzing up our website or keeping our accounts in check, Layal's got the knack for making things look good and run smoothly.</div>
<a href="https://lclettry.com" class="credits-link" target="_blank"><span class="link-text">View Portfolio</span><span class="link-line"></span></a>
